SQL_STMT_U.val: select T2.GroupID, len(STRING_AGG(CONCAT_WS('|',isnull(T2.BaseEntry,0), isnull(T2.BaseType,0), isnull(T2.BaseEntrySAP,0) ), '/')) as LengthKey, STRING_AGG(CONCAT_WS('|',isnull(T2.BaseEntry,0), isnull(T2.BaseType,0), isnull(T2.BaseEntrySAP,0) ), '/') as BaseDocKey, count(1) as total from ( select (ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY R.InvoiceId) - 1) / 100 as GroupID, R.DocEntry as BaseEntry, R.InvType as BaseType, H.DocEntrySAP as BaseEntrySAP from rct2 R left join H_DocEntry H on R.DocEntry = H.DocEntry and R.InvType = H.ObjType and H.DataType = 'C' where R.docnum = :1 ) T2 group by T2.GroupID
